        "title": "Generating and Opening a PDF file",
        "body": "<p>I am trying to generate a PDF file and open it after generation in a new window so that users can print it. I have below code which generates the pdf and saves it on the disk, but having trouble opening it.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>PdfWriter.getInstance(document, new FileOutputStream(\"HelloWorld-Table.pdf\"));\ndocument.open();\n\nPdfPTable table = new PdfPTable(3); // 3 columns.\n\nPdfPCell cell1 = new PdfPCell(new Paragraph(\"Cell 1\"));\nPdfPCell cell2 = new PdfPCell(new Paragraph(\"Cell 2\"));\nPdfPCell cell3 = new PdfPCell(new Paragraph(\"Cell 3\"));\n\ntable.addCell(cell1);\ntable.addCell(cell2);\ntable.addCell(cell3);\n\ndocument.add(table);\ndocument.close();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>What can I add here so that it opens the PDF file?<\/p>\n",
